launch 2 ec2 instances for blue and green
install nginx in both server
yum update -y
yum intall nginx if its linux ec2
go to cd /usr/share/nginx/html and edit default index.html and add ur custom website contents
if via httpd web server, do yum update -y, yum install -y httpd, cd /var/www/html
edit vi index.html
systemctl start nginx, enable nginx, status nginx
netstat -ntlp
if ur code is stored in github or s3 bucket- wget http://webserverash.s3.amazonaws.com/index1.html
zip files in desktop and copy the zipped folder to bucket
always ensure u copy the .html u want to the html folder in nginx
change default nginx file by adding contents from index1.html and index0.html from terraform

add 2 instanes to Load balancer add tgs and refresh dns of LB to see traffic swicthing from blue to green
